<p class="lead">We are the Sunseeker Solar Car Project, a team of students from <a href="https://www.wmich.edu/" target="_blank">Western Michigan University</a> in Kalamazoo, Michigan. We design, build, and race our <a href="{{ url_prefix }}/our-car">solar powered vehicle</a> in the <a href="http://americansolarchallenge.org" target="_blank">American Solar Challenge</a> and Formula Sun Grand Prix. Continue reading below to learn more about our organization.</p>
